data.description: This spacious home has an inviting front patio, updated flooring, painting cabinets in the kitchen, gas cooktop, large dining area, plenty of storage too.  The back yard features a covered patio, a large metal building, and a second storage building.  This home is also in an X flood zone and eligible for RD financing.  Make this great home yours today!
